lyrics:
[verse]
Keith Whitley, a legend filled with pain
His voice like whiskey, pouring through the rain
A restless spirit, now forever gone
His songs still echo, carrying on strong

[chorus]
Blake, Jon, Luke, raise your voices high
In tribute to a man who touched the sky
Keith Whitley's memory, we won't let it fade
Forever singing his songs, in the country music parade
style: Blake Shelton Jon Pardi Luke Bryan
